== 製作 ==
2015年10月，官方證實由於《[[安娜貝爾_(電影)|安娜貝爾]]》票房上的成功，而決定推出續集<ref name="Annabelle2">{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/annabelle-2/|title='Annabelle 2' is on the Way, So Burn Your Doll Collection Now|website=[[安娜貝爾：造孽/Film|安娜貝爾：造孽//Film]]|first=Jacob|last=Hall|date=2015-10-19|access-date=2016-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924142526/http://www.slashfilm.com/annabelle-2|archive-date=2016-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[大衛·F·桑德柏格|大衛·F·桑德柏格]]取代了[[約翰·R·李昂尼提|約翰·R·李昂尼提]]成為續集的導演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/annabelle-2-lights-out-director-david-sandberg-1201736596/|title='Annabelle 2' Draws 'Lights Out' Director David Sandberg|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Dave|last=McNary|date=2016-03-22|access-date=2016-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916040208/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/annabelle-2-lights-out-director-david-sandberg-1201736596/|archive-date=2016-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。前集的編劇蓋瑞·道柏曼回歸撰寫劇本，而{{le|彼得·沙佛朗|Peter Safran}}和[[溫子仁|溫子仁]]也會再度擔任監製。2016年6月，演員{{le|史蒂芬妮·席格曼|Stephanie Sigman}}、[[米蘭達·奧圖|米蘭達·奧圖]]與[[泰莉莎·貝特曼|泰莉莎·貝特曼]]加入劇組<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/stephanie-sigman-annabelle-2-spectre-1201801416/|title='Spectre' Actress Stephanie Sigman to Star in 'Annabelle' Sequel (EXCLUSIVE)|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Justin|last=Kroll|date=2016-06-22|accessdate=2016-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623141227/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/stephanie-sigman-annabelle-2-spectre-1201801416/|archive-date=2016-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/maggie-grace-supercon-category-5-talitha-bateman-annabelle-2-1201779256/|title=Maggie Grace Joins Comedy Heist Pic 'Supercon'; Talitha Bateman Joins 'Annabelle 2'|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Ross A.|last=Lincoln|date=2016-06-24|accessdate=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628103646/http://deadline.com/2016/06/maggie-grace-supercon-category-