=== 拍攝 ===
電影正式於2016年6月27日在[[加利福尼亞|加利福尼亞]]的[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]開拍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/movie/3397064/set-annabelle-2/|title=Even More Dolls On the Set of 'Annabelle 2'|website=[[Bloody_Disgusting|Bloody Disgusting]]|first=Brad|last=Miska|date=2016-06-30|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701133208/http://bloody-disgusting.com/movie/3397064/set-annabelle-2/|archive-date=2016-07-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/the-annabelle-2-cast-expands-as-filming-begins-770|title=The Annabelle 2 Cast Expands as Filming Begins|website=[[Joblo|Joblo]]|first=Cody|last=Hamman|date=2016-06-30|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701134314/http://www.joblo.com/horror-movies/news/the-annabelle-2-cast-expands-as-filming-begins-770|archive-date=2016-07-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於2016年8月15日宣布[[殺青|殺青]]<ref>{{cite tweet|number=765377507096788996|title=That's a wrap on Annabelle 2! Thank you to the awesome cast and crew! In theaters May 2017.|author=David F. Sandberg|author-link=David F. Sandberg|user=ponysmasher|date=2016-08-15|accessdate=2016-08-16}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《安娜貝爾：造孽》由[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]定於2017年5月19日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/ben-affleck-live-by-night-release-date-annabelle-2-1201736057/|title=Ben Affleck's Crime Drama 'Live by Night,' 3 More Warner Bros. Films Dated for 2017|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Dave|last=McNary|date=2016-03-22|access-date=2016-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924131039/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/ben-affleck-live-by-night-release-date-annabelle-2-1201736057/|archive-date=2016-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，美國上映日延期至8月11日。

===評價===
《安娜貝爾：造孽》獲得了正面居多的評價，主要認為電影的各方面比前集進步許多。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於100條評論，新鮮度69%，平均得分6.2／10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/annabelle_creation|title=Annabelle: Creation (2017)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2017-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807125330/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/annabelle_creation|archive-date=2017-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，則獲得了62分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/annabelle-creation|title=Annabelle: Creation reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2017-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819110017/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/annabelle-creation|archive-date=2017-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾在A+至F間的評價落在「B」，這與前集《安娜貝爾》的分數相同<ref name="opening" />。

===票房===
在美國，《安娜貝爾：造孽》與《{{le|堅果行動2|The Nut Job 2: Nutty by Nature}}》、《[[玻璃城堡_(電影)|玻璃城堡]]》同時上映、競爭，《安娜貝爾：造孽》預估餘首週末能從3502間戲院中獲得3000萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/annabelle-creation-nutjob-2-dunkirk-box-office-preview-1202145555/|title='Annabelle: Creation' Will Be This Summer's Last Scream At The B.O. With Estimated $30M+ Opening – Preview|first=Anthony|last=D'Allesandro|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-08-09|access-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812035306/http://deadline.com/2017/08/annabelle-creation-nutjob-2-dunkirk-box-office-preview-1202145555/|archive-date=2017-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影在週四晚間獲得了400萬美元的票房，這比前集的210萬美元還高出許多<ref name="opening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/annabelle-creation-dark-tower-dunkirk-1202147007/|title='Annabelle: Creation' Comes Alive On Thursday With $4M|first=Anthony|last=D'Allesandro|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-08-11|access-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6siVzpOAa?url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/annabelle-creation-dark-tower-dunkirk-1202147007/|archive-date=2017-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/box-office/box-office-annabelle-creation-nabs-4-million-in-thursday-pre-shows-1202523758/|title=Box Office: 'Annabelle: Creation' Nabs $4 Million on Thursday Night|first=Brent|last=Lang|website=Variety|date=2017-08-11|access-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812140003/http://variety.com/2017/film/box-office/box-office-annabelle-creation-nabs-4-million-in-thursday-pre-shows-1202523758/|archive-date=2017-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首週末票房為3500萬美元，位居當週冠軍<ref name="opening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/annabelle-creation-dark-tower-dunkirk-1202147007/|title='Annabelle: Creation' Comes Alive On Thursday With $4M|first=Anthony|last=D'Allesandro|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-08-11|access-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6siVzpOAa?url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/annabelle-creation-dark-tower-dunkirk-1202147007/|archive-date=2017-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

